  <official_title>A Phase II, Open Label, Multi-center, Multi-arm Study of Ceritinib in Patients With Advanced Solid Tumors and Hematological Malignancies Characterized by Genetic Abnormalities of Anaplastic Lymphoma Kinase (ALK)</official_title>
